<lb n="0354c29"/>普德<note n="0354014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">像＝象【三】【宮】</note><note n="0354014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">像＝象【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0354014"><lem>像</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">象</rdg></app>佛　南無無憂德佛　南無優波羅
<pb ed="T" id="T14.0444.0355a" n="0355a"/>
<lb n="0355a01"/>香佛　南無大地佛　南無大龍德佛　南無
<lb n="0355a02"/>清淨王佛　南無<note n="0355001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">廣念＝大愛【三】</note><note n="0355001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">廣念＝大愛【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0355001"><lem>廣念</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">大愛</rdg></app>佛　南無蓮花德佛
