<lb n="0355a11"/><note n="0355003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">瑳＝蹉【三】【宮】</note><note n="0355003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">瑳＝蹉【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0355003"><lem>瑳</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">蹉</rdg></app>德佛　南無佛天佛　南無師子幢佛
